text: Nicholas Harrison (born 1964) is an English theoretical physicist. Nicholas Harrison or Nick Harrison may also refer to: *Nicholas Harrison (athlete) (born 1970), Australian long-distance runner *Nick Harrison (cricketer) (born 1992), English cricketer *Nick Harrison (racing) (1982–2019), American stock car racing crew chief *Nick Harrison, a character on Shortland Street
title: Nicholas Harrison (disambiguation)
